Renren here!

394
00:23:40,833 --> 00:23:43,041
Coming up on
<i>First Love Monster</i> .

395
00:23:43,125 --> 00:23:44,500
[mumbling incoherently]

396
00:23:44,583 --> 00:23:46,166
